+
+ * EC provides:
+ * - Chipset temperature
+ * - CPU temperature
+ * - Motherboard temperature
+ * - T_Sensor temperature
+ * - VRM temperature
+ * - Water In temperature
+ * - Water Out temperature
+ * - CPU Optional fan RPM
+ * - Chipset fan RPM
+ * - VRM Heat Sink fan RPM
